vo_full_103202-5-12"},{"narration":"「调成什么味道都无所谓@赶紧把你们觉得可怜的自己拖出来@就那样吞噬掉吧」","voiceFullAuto":"fullvoice/section_103202/vo_full_103202-5-13"},{"autoTurnLast":0.2,"narrationEffect":"out"},{"nameNarration":"御魂","narration":"―御魂―@但是，不管如何俯瞰@毁灭神滨市的我都不会消失","narrationAnchor":"bottom","narrationCoverOpacity":110,"narrationEffect":"in","narrationFontSize":30,"narrationLineMargin":10,"narrationLineSpace":20,"voiceFullAuto":"fullvoice/section_103202/vo_full_103202-5-14"},{"narration":"―御魂―@而且，如果吞噬了这份悲伤@就等同于失去我自己","voiceFullAuto":"fullvoice/section_103202/vo_full_103202-5-15"},{"nameNarration":"十七夜","narration":"―十七夜―@…或许的确如此吧","voiceFullAuto":"fullvoice/section_103202/vo_full_103202-5-16"},{"bgm":"stop","narration":"―十七夜―@但是，八云@事情或许其实并非如此","voiceFullAuto":"fullvoice/section_103202/vo_full_103202-5-17"},{"nameNarration":"御魂","narration":"―御魂―@十七夜…？","voiceFullAuto":"fullvoice/section_103202/vo_full_103202-5-18"},{"bgm":"bgm05_event06","nameNarration":"十七夜","narration":"―十七夜―@我们要毁灭@被自己心中的悲伤填满的神滨市","voiceFullAuto":"fullvoice/section_103202/vo_full_103202-5-19"},{"narration":"―十七夜―@然后，接下来要与@想要共同前行的神滨市一起活下去","voiceFullAuto":"fullvoice/section_103202/vo_full_103202-5-20"},{"nameNarration":"御魂","narration":"―御魂―@和咪她们维系起的神滨市一起…？","voiceFullAuto":"fullvoice/section_103202/vo_full_103202-5-21"},{"nameNarration":"十七夜","narration":"―十七夜―@是的，为此@我们必须吞噬掉旧的自己","voiceFullAuto":"fullvoice/section_103202/vo_full_103202-5-22"},{"nameNarration":"御魂","narration":"―御魂―@…然后将其化为自己的食粮，对吧","voiceFullAuto":"fullvoice/section_103202/vo_full_103202-5-23"},{"nameNarration":"十七夜","narration":"―十七夜―@唔姆，就算是为了未来@被悲伤囚禁的状况也必须到此为止","voiceFullAuto":"fullvoice/section_103202/vo_full_103202-5-24"},{"nameNarration":"御魂","narration":"―御魂―@…我知道了","voiceFullAuto":"fullvoice/section_103202/vo_full_103202-5-25"},{"narration":"―御魂―@为了咪维系起的明天@我也会吞噬过去","voiceFullAuto":"fullvoice/section_103202/vo_full_103202-5-26"},{"autoTurnLast":0.5,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_020.exp3.json","id":101600,"motion":0,"pos":0},{"cheek":0,"fa